# VMT Scenario Configuration

## Scenario Files

- **Location:** [scenarios/](mdc:scenarios/) directory
- **Format:** YAML configuration files
- **Schema:** Defined in [src/scenarios/schema.py](mdc:src/scenarios/schema.py)
- **Loader:** [src/scenarios/loader.py](mdc:src/scenarios/loader.py)

## Key Configuration Sections

### Basic Parameters
```yaml
grid_size: 40                    # NÃ—N grid
agent_count: 20                  # Number of agents
max_steps: 200                   # Simulation length
seed: 42                        # Random seed for reproducibility
```

### Exchange Regimes
```yaml
params:
  exchange_regime: "mixed"       # barter_only | money_only | mixed | mixed_liquidity_gated
  mode_schedule: "both"         # trade | forage | both
```

### Agent Configuration
```yaml
initial_inventories:
  A: [10, 5, 8]                 # Starting goods A
  B: [5, 10, 7]                 # Starting goods B  
  M: [100, 50, 75]              # Starting money (if money regime)

utilities:
  mix:
    - type: "CES"
      params: {rho: 0.5, w_A: 0.6, w_B: 0.4}
      weight: 0.7
    - type: "Linear" 
      params: {v_A: 1.0, v_B: 0.8}
      weight: 0.3
```

